        Gas Appliance Compliance When Selling a Brisbane Property
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Gas cooktops, hot water systems, instantaneous heaters, and fireplaces each carry compliance considerations at sale. Here is what Queensland sellers should check before listing, and what buyers and their building and pest inspectors will look for.
      </p>
    </div>
